(6758, 'Kamagra oral jelly', 'كاماجرا جيل بالفم', '', '24', 'Sildenafil', 'Farmacia', 'Unknown', 'غير محدد', 'مقوي للرجال', 'Tonic for men', '', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
